This paper deals with regression problems and variable selection, which are common topics in machine learning and statistics. The use of the group Lasso method also suggests a focus on structured sparsity, which is often studied in the context of machine learning and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.ST (Statistics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
